<view class="container">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="hero-title">房产参考价计算器</view>
    <view class="hero-sub">基于租金回报率、市场比价与指导价的多维度参考工具</view>
    <view class="hero-tip">数据由您自行输入，本地计算，不采集隐私</view>
  </view>

  <view class="feature-list">
    <view class="feature-item">
      <view class="feature-icon">📊</view>
      <view class="feature-text">
        <view class="feature-title">租金回报率法</view>
        <view class="feature-desc">根据租金收益反推房产合理参考价</view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="feature-item">
      <view class="feature-icon">🏠</view>
      <view class="feature-text">
        <view class="feature-title">市场比价法</view>
        <view class="feature-desc">参考同小区成交均价与房屋属性修正</view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="feature-item">
      <view class="feature-icon">📋</view>
      <view class="feature-text">
        <view class="feature-title">指导价参考法</view>
        <view class="feature-desc">结合公开指导价进行参考测算</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="btn-primary" bindtap="goToInput">开始测算</view>

  <view wx:if="{{hasCache}}" class="cache-card" bindtap="goToResult">
    <view class="cache-label">上次测算</view>
    <view class="cache-value">{{cacheSummary}}</view>
    <view class="cache-action">查看结果 ></view>
  </view>

  <view class="disclaimer">
    本工具仅供参考，不构成任何投资建议、房产评估报告或交易依据。实际交易请以专业评估和市场行情为准。
  </view>
</view>
